                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830430-18-off95 t17830430-18-cd96"></join> last, two linen shirts, value 4 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17830430-18-victim267" type="victimName">
                     Edward 
                     Humphrys
